node.text:
The Peacock bite was on fire today! Caught 16 in one hour, along with a 5lb Largemouth Bass & a Mayan Cichlid! Caught one of my hook-ups on video with my phone in my shorts 🤣 Too much fun!
#peacock #bass #peacockbass #crotchcam #freshwaterfishing #freshwater #bassfishing

node.text:
This is what makes fish tagging & research so freaking cool!!@tagdolphinfish This dolphin fish/mahi mahi was previously tagged & released off Summerland Key just 4 days before it was caught aboard Bombchelle off of Boynton Beach! She traveled approximately 187 miles in just 4 days (about 45 miles per day)!! No wonder these fish are the fastest growing fish in the ocean! Talk about a one track mind.. *Eat, swim, repeat* 
Please swipe through the pictures to read more! Big thank you to Wess Merten for sharing the data! 
Join us in this research effort & order your tagging kit at dolphintagging.com/tags
@captainmarkfl @pelagicgear
